MUSIC THERAPY: TYPE AND BENEFITS FOR ANXIETY, DEPRESSION AND MORE

Music therapy involves using a person\'s responses and connections to music to stimulate positive changes in mood and overall well-being. Music therapy can include creating music with instruments of all kinds, singing, moving to music, or simply listening to music.

Relaxing anti stress music to control anxiety and eliminate stress. Zen music with Piano to relax or meditate. Beautiful nature landscapes with calming music for relaxation and meditation. Beautiful Relaxing Piano Music for Calm
